    And I should see following search entity types:
      | Type     | N | isSelected |
      | All      | 2 | yes        |
      | Products | 2 |            |
    And number of records should be 2
    And I should see following search results:
      | Title                     | Type    |
      | PSKU1 - Product 1         | Product |
      | PSKU_KIT1 - Product Kit 1 | Product |

